public class CorrelatedNotificationValueImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.oss.fm.monitor.CorrelatedNotificationValue

CorrelatedNotificationValueImpl Represents the implementation of a correlated notification identifier. Correlated notifications in one server can be distinguished by a notification ID and a managed object instance.
